  <summary date="2005-06-28T20:14:07Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Realistic Roofing Tax Treatment Act of 2005 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) classify as 20-year property for depreciation purposes any roof system which meets the requirements of Standard 90.1-2004 of the American Society of Heating, Refrigerating, and Air Conditioning Engineers; and (2) require use of the straight line method for depreciation of such property.</summary>
